define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_CONFIGURARGALERIA",    '<b>Configure A Gallery Presentation:</b><br>This is your presentation stylesheet for displaying images in each gallery. Sections include choices for displaying descriptions, allowing voting and comments, defining width and heights of images, borders, picture frame styles, thumbnail presentation, categories and subgalleries, and more!');
