define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_SUBGALERIAS",'<table><tr><td></td><td>SubGallery </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>The subgalleries make it easy to put the images in any one gallery into subgroups. For example, your JUNGLE gallery could contain subgalleries of Animals, Birds, and Fish.');
define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_ANADIRSUBGALERIAS",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Enter the name of the subgallery and click Add Subgallery.<br>The subgalleries make it easy to put the images in any one gallery into subgalleries. For example, your JUNGLE gallery could contain subgalleries of Animals, Birds, and Fish. To apply the subgallery names you create here to the individual images in this gallery, proceed to to Change Photos and Descriptions, select this gallery, and apply the appropriate subgallery to each image.');
define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_ELIMINARSUBGALERIAS",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Select the name of the subgallery you want to delete and click Delete Subgallery. Note that images assigned to this subgallery are not deleted from the gallery, just the subgallery classification is removed.');
define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_ELIMINARCATEGORIA",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Select the category name you want to delete and click Delete Category.');
define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_NOMBRECATEGORIA",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Enter the name of the category you want to create and click Save Category. Categories are ways to classify several galleries into a group. The groups will show as headings in the dropdown menu selection for galleries. To apply the Category to the galleries, proceed to the Configure a Gallery Presentation, select the gallery, and at the bottom of the page, select the appropriate category you have created here.');

define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_CATEGORIASSELECCIONADAS",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Active categories for the gallery.');
define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_CATEGORIASNOSELECCIONADAS",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Categories NOT active for the gallery.');

define("_HELP_USKOLAXGALLERY_CATEGORIAS",'<table><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp; </td> <td></td></tr></table><br>Categories are ways to classify several galleries into a group. The groups will show as headings in the dropdown menu selection for galleries. For example, you might group different galleries together by Photographer, or perhaps by Medium (photos, paintings, drawings.)');

